body:
Okay sorry but after increasing my swap partition with gparted to fix another error and running the command with --jobs 4 I get this `libtensorflow_demo.so` was not created error again.

Logs: [output1.txt](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/files/243192/output1.txt)

This is the command I executed:
`sudo bazel build //tensorflow/examples/android:tensorflow_demo --verbose_failures --jobs 4 >output2.txt 2>&1`
